{"tid":565670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「呆」出冠軍來！國際發呆比賽3月尾登陸香港","createTime":"2018-02-19T08:21:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T10:29:01.000Z","uid":167984,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"019ff4327f31475e6f77a42f83ff99bd298f2a15","tid":565670,"uid":167984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T08:21:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://sportsroad.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/spaceout_20180126-005.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsportsroad.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2Fspaceout_20180126-005.jpg&h=5919a41e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://sportsroad.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/spaceout_20180126-002.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsportsroad.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2Fspaceout_20180126-002.png&h=2e41a519&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「國際發呆比賽」發源於韓國，之前已經在北京、荷蘭及台灣等地舉行。發呆比賽的主辦單位日前於Facebook開設專頁，並公布比賽將於3月31日登陸香港。香港站賽事將於中環海濱摩天輪旁的 AIA Vitality Park舉行，屆時80個參賽者必須於90分鐘內徹底放空並穩定維持放空狀態，最後由現場觀眾投票及心跳穩定等因素定勝負，搶奪首個「香港發呆王」稱號。主辦單位指由於香港多次被選為最高壓力和不愉快城市，「為鼓勵一眾港人減壓，特意引入國際發呆比賽，推廣發呆和放空的重要性」，到時並會有連串精彩表演及活動，為香港營造一個繁忙都市人必到的大型發呆嘉年華。<br />\n<br />\n香港人早前也曾經在「國際發呆比賽」揚威，科技大學學生陳棨豪在去年年尾的台灣站成功擊敗其他參賽者，奪得「第5屆國際發呆王」稱號。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://sportsroad.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/spaceout_20180126-001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsportsroad.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2Fspaceout_20180126-001.jpg&h=dd53aae4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n科大學生陳棨豪在台灣站贏出。（發呆比賽台灣站Facebook圖片）"},{"pid":"981fcd9539e832754d3f81dfb4cf36c8d93c88e5","tid":565670,"uid":49197,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T08:24:11.000Z","msg":"馬明參賽贏硬"},{"pid":"8326561143776218e1ab9dec575c96442ce560b4","tid":565670,"uid":167984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T08:25:20.000Z","msg":"熱話<br />\n【機會嚟啦！】國際發呆大賽3月香港舉行　唔准笑講嘢同瞓覺<br />\n撰文： 楊羨庭<br />\n發佈日期：2018-01-25 17:59<br />\n最後更新日期：2018-01-25 21:18<br />\n<br />\n    當「做多錯多」的風氣蔓延，放空發呆似乎是最佳活動！源自韓國的發呆比賽，自2014年舉行第一屆後反應熱烈，近年逐漸變成國際性比賽，而本港科大學生陳棨豪早前更在台灣站勇奪冠軍殊榮，而今屆發呆比賽將移師香港舉行，自問最愛放空、發呆大過天的朋友機會嚟喇！3月底各路呆人在中環海濱摩天輪決一高下！<br />\n<br />\n首屆國際發呆比賽在2014年於韓國舉行。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n「發呆比賽香港站」facebook專頁發帖指，香港多次被選為最高壓力和不愉快城市，為鼓勵一眾港人減壓，特意從韓國引入國際發呆比賽，並在3月底於中環海濱摩天輪舉行，為港人帶來發呆體驗。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲規則很簡單，參賽者須在90分鐘內徹底放空並穩定維持放空狀態，參賽期間不可笑、聊天甚至睡覺，最後由現場觀眾投票及心跳穩定等因素決定勝負。帖文一出，已吸引不少網民標籤朋友組隊參與，專頁表示參賽名額只有80人，將於2月開放公眾報名。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去年10月中，台北市亦有舉行發呆比賽，港產片《志明與春嬌》系列導演彭浩翔，成為其中一名到台灣比賽的港人，他在個人facebook專頁曾上載練習發呆的短片，誓要「為港爭光」，未知他今次會否在主場出戰。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1061586/xlarge/957ce7d8f49975c903cad10fafba68bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1061586%2Fxlarge%2F957ce7d8f49975c903cad10fafba68bf.jpg&h=568d54b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1061586/xlarge/957ce7d8f49975c903cad10fafba68bf.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1061586%2Fxlarge%2F957ce7d8f49975c903cad10fafba68bf.jpg&d=0skjTMQjnkPTMpFpIFFVWwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=4ba3491a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1061586/xlarge/957ce7d8f49975c903cad10fafba68bf.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"c6a1f35c5709041617dbf1ef7e35372c94b56e71","tid":565670,"uid":35870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T08:25:30.000Z","msg":"揾班玩慣meditation/打坐嘅去，應該屈機"},{"pid":"76929c9eee31a244f4b0a1eac4385f4602bcbd6a","tid":565670,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T08:26:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>揾班玩慣meditation/打坐嘅去，應該屈機</blockquote><br />\n或者瑜珈個類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c877613c7e327108f0bff788d532e3907a618032","tid":565670,"uid":107656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T08:26:23.000Z","msg":"咁咪要90分鐘唔眨眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cffeea3d024e43bbe52a678b4174614dc50afddc","tid":565670,"uid":167984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T08:27:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/153156/thumbnail/d3d2d856b9b0ddb4fb8c141a8bbec564.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F153156%2Fthumbnail%2Fd3d2d856b9b0ddb4fb8c141a8bbec564.jpg&h=ba2e6f32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/890244/xlarge/a0b0f459c7e68f48c05a786974071f2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F890244%2Fxlarge%2Fa0b0f459c7e68f48c05a786974071f2c.jpg&h=7516e899&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e68ecb9246c454f64426a54c117b266aa2f9b058","tid":565670,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T08:54:14.000Z","msg":"好無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dddec8d682d369ffd5f98af443f218a402ce61c7","tid":565670,"uid":104387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T09:04:25.000Z","msg":"政府d狗官可唔可以參加"},{"pid":"4dea825c21a0b77d4fe932a6ce515ce1c16b7c2e","tid":565670,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dddec8d682d369ffd5f98af443f218a402ce61c7","tid":565670,"uid":104387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T09:04:25.000Z","msg":"政府d狗官可唔可以參加"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T09:09:42.000Z","msg":"議員就得 班功能組別平時都on99咁架啦"},{"pid":"b29b68cc9ee948aaf889262c356989f4fe1dfb28","tid":565670,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4dea825c21a0b77d4fe932a6ce515ce1c16b7c2e","tid":565670,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dddec8d682d369ffd5f98af443f218a402ce61c7","tid":565670,"uid":104387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T09:04:25.000Z","msg":"政府d狗官可唔可以參加"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T09: